Class Controller.cases

java.lang.Object

Enclosing class:
Controller
public static class Controller.cases
extends java.lang.Object
This Class is responsible for Task A1/A2. Contains the following attributes for a specified date: country name, total number of confirmed cases, total number of confirmed cases per 1 Million.
